show.description: Ek shraapit devta ki nazar jismein jo dekhe uski kismat badal jaati hai, insaan aur bhagya ke beech ka khel hai. Jab mohabbat aur shraap takraate hain, to har rishta ek imtihaan ban jaata hai .
